Made this twice to raves both times. Prefered tang of Buttermilk Blue to the Gorgonzola. Threw all ingredients into the casserole together the first time having misplaced the recipe; covered it in the oven for 25 minutes and finished off uncovered. No perceptible difference from doing it per the recipe the second time. Go figure!

