Oh my gosh, I can't believe how wonderful this is! My family gobbled this up and even my husband, who usually is quite a picky eater, had seconds. As previous reviewers have said, don't skimp on the blue cheese. I used the best I could find and then added a bit extra because I love the taste. (For those who live in Buffalo, go to Wegmans or Premier Gourmet) Wonderful, comforting side dish.

